{"tid":858444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"向現屆政府表示無比嘅敬意","createTime":"2018-10-11T22:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T02:06:14.000Z","uid":14175,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d97897af158e373f39a3770336722eedca700cd","tid":858444,"uid":14175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:33:11.000Z","msg":"現屆政府為香港貢獻良多<br />\n為表我對佢地嘅尊重港人<br />\n特意寫咗幾多佢表達心聲<br />\n文筆唔好請各位多多包涵<br />\n<br />\n官看完今年嘅屍政包膠，<br />\n商信凸首已經盡佢所能。<br />\n鄉港定必再創更多高峰，<br />\n黑苦嘅環境即將成過去。<br />\n民主喺香港從未消失過，<br />\n不知所謂嘅港豬勿亂港。<br />\n聊事鬥非嘅廢青正垃圾，<br />\n生舊叉燒好過生著廢青。<br />\n漠講話民主一直都存在，<br />\n視非黑白都仲係咁黑白。<br />\n民族意識秉承共產主義，<br />\n意見立場一致撐習大大。<br />\n凸別多謝眾多高貴官員，<br />\n首要目的係要攪好香港。<br />\n林太嘅付出實在係太多，<br />\n鄭重地表達萬分的敬意。<br />\n我知你地為香港辛苦喇，<br />\n𨳒弟讀書唔多文筆好差。<br />\n你地最重要收到份心意，<br />\n老天一定會保佑住你地。<br />\n母須過份擔心收尾幾年。"},{"pid":"4a910f534b43c4be6ce065e53865a5376e38478b","tid":858444,"uid":14175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c509a1a3c927fdc9fdba3990589cb9a55b930331","tid":858444,"uid":83555,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:41:12.000Z","msg":"你出發點係好<br />\n但我真係睇到好撚尷尬"},{"pid":"07c40e4fdfbf0415fd6e99cfa945b948a530aa74","tid":858444,"uid":14175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T22:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a613c95641cf98d0e44465ccee7bec89ca04dd71","tid":858444,"uid":124466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"床頭詩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9003b21a86939ad1c1717d3ab0b510c461ce930e","tid":858444,"uid":206673,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:21:04.000Z","msg":"邊間教會？"},{"pid":"9a1654cfcf3dce4bc5a8df67128134265cdd42e6","tid":858444,"uid":182110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:40:37.000Z","msg":"官<br />\n商<br />\n鄉<br />\n黑<br />\n民<br />\n不<br />\n聊<br />\n生<br />\n漠<br />\n視<br />\n民<br />\n意<br />\n凸<br />\n首<br />\n林<br />\n鄭<br />\n我<br />\n𨳒<br />\n你<br />\n老"},{"pid":"255c9acd19aef12caf2eef03448622958ff3c298","tid":858444,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:45:20.000Z","msg":"隱題詩係小學雞岩岩學覺得好得意好撚勁先玩"},{"pid":"a2bde2f315d3db0fe1e837460e6c6d0d94ac9fe3","tid":858444,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"做多左啦，睇見都尷尬"},{"pid":"cf1dd6a3c71867724bbbf6b168e26b402a119379","tid":858444,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T02:06:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬咁勁 林鄭實嚇到跳起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}